title._content: Mess call at the planting camp on Lookout Mountain, Columbia National Forest, Washington, 1936

description._content: Original Collection: Gerald W. Williams Collection Item Number: WilliamsG:CCC mess call Image Description: The ringing tone of the metal triangle is a welcome sound to the hungry men after a day's work in the open air.
